133
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:36,799
Alright.

134
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,120
Then let's see who's tougher.

135
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,720
Our boys are no pushovers,

136
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:40,879
