251
00:14:05,279 --> 00:14:06,399
And there's no match tomorrow.

252
00:14:06,679 --> 00:14:07,399
Have a little, just a little.

253
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:08,480
Just a little.

254
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:09,440
A small drink won't hurt.

255
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:10,759
Have some.

256
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:14,559
Come on.

257
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:15,320
Uncle.

258
00:14:15,759 --> 00:14:16,080
Okay.

259
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:17,840
Here, welcome.

260
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:18,240
Auntie.

261
00:14:18,279 --> 00:14:18,720
Welcome.

262
00:14:18,759 --> 00:14:19,279
Welcome.

263
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,080
Cheers!

264
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:26,879
I'd like to ask,

265
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,399
