295
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:26,919
As the saying goes,

296
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:28,799
build your career first,

297
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:29,960
then start a family.

298
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:30,279
Right.

299
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:30,799
Isn't that so?

300
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:31,919
If you don't build a career,

301
00:15:32,039 --> 00:15:33,120
how can you support a family?

302
00:15:34,559 --> 00:15:36,080
If you don't build a career, you...

303
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:36,799
What are you on about?

304
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,879
Future stuff can wait.

305
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:39,960
Eat first.

306
00:15:40,159 --> 00:15:40,960
Have some food.

307
00:15:44,399 --> 00:15:44,720
Yaoyao,

308
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:45,559
do you remember

309
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:46,559
your Uncle Peng?

310
00:15:47,879 --> 00:15:49,399
He just opened a car dealership,

311
00:15:49,679 --> 00:15:51,039
all imported luxury cars.

312
00:15:51,279 --> 00:15:51,600
How about this:

313
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:52,879
let me introduce you,

314
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:53,879
and you can start

315
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,519
working in sales for a while.

316
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:56,639
How about it?

317
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:58,879
Give it a try.

318
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,559
Uncle Peng is a real expert

319
00:16:00,559 --> 00:16:01,360
when it comes to business.

320
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:02,120
If you work with him,

321
00:16:02,279 --> 00:16:03,360
you'll definitely learn a lot.

322
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:04,039
What do you say?

323
00:16:10,159 --> 00:16:10,519
Uncle,

324
00:16:11,799 --> 00:16:12,320
thank you, Uncle.

325
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:14,120
Thank you, Auntie.

326
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:14,600
You're welcome.

327
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:16,679
But

328
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,399
right now I want to put my energy

329
00:16:19,399 --> 00:16:21,799
into the Jiangsu Super League.

330
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:23,679
So for now,

331
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:25,360
I'll have to put that off.

332
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:26,080
Hold on,

333
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:27,440
I'm just worried you'll miss this chance

334
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:28,519
and won't get another one.

335
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,720
It's his first time here,

336
00:16:30,840 --> 00:16:32,240
and you're grilling him with questions.

337
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:34,679
Yaoyao,

338
00:16:35,039 --> 00:16:35,879
tell us,

339
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:36,919
how did you two meet?

340
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:37,759
The two of us?

341
00:16:38,519 --> 00:16:39,399
Do you remember

342
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:40,600
when I was in college,

343
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:41,919
I joined the cheerleading squad?

344
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:43,080
Back then,

345
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:44,679
his team needed cheerleaders,

346
00:16:44,919 --> 00:16:45,559
so I went.

347
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:47,279
You have no idea

348
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,559
how handsome he was.

349
00:16:48,799 --> 00:16:49,759
When he was on the field,

350
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:51,000
I was totally smitten.

351
00:16:51,919 --> 00:16:52,840
So every day

352
00:16:52,879 --> 00:16:54,600
I'd wait for him outside the field,

353
00:16:55,159 --> 00:16:56,120
and that's how I got him.

354
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:57,200
You silly girl,

355
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,080
have you no shame?

356
00:17:01,679 --> 00:17:02,679
Life, you know,

357
00:17:04,759 --> 00:17:05,759
always throws all kinds

358
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,440
of surprises your way.

359
00:17:10,799 --> 00:17:11,720
Eat, eat, eat.

360
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:13,240
Uncle.

361
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:13,880
Come on, come on.

362
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:14,519
Here.
